    {
      "lineNumber": 4,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 5,
      "text": "January 31, 1949",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 6,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 7,
      "text": "Mr. J. Edgar Hoover",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 8,
      "text": "Washington D.C.",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 9,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 10,
      "text": "Dear Mr. Hoover:",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 11,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 12,
      "text": "Here is a bit of information which may be of great signi-",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 13,
      "text": "ficance, or may be merely an observation of a scientific experi-",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 14,
      "text": "ment. It may be known by military authorities and the A.E.C. or",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 15,
      "text": "only a few may have seen it and none reported it to the right",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 16,
      "text": "place. Here it is. Can you pass it to the right persons?",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 17,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 18,
      "text": "Last May one afternoon I saw four beams in the sky passing",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 19,
      "text": "from the northwest to the southeast and converging in the",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 20,
      "text": "Cascade mountains. In those four narrow beams small clouds were",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 21,
      "text": "forming. And where the beams met apparently against the mountains",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 22,
      "text": "a great explosion effect was to be seen. I would say that they",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 23,
      "text": "were visible for at least 10 minutes or longer.",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 24,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 25,
      "text": "The sight brought to mind an article read before the war",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 26,
      "text": "about experiments carried on in Europe with various types of",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 27,
      "text": "radio beams to effect rainfall. I would guess that I had seen",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 28,
      "text": "the article in the Science Digest.",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 29,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 30,
      "text": "The Columbia River flood of last summer and the unusual",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 31,
      "text": "precipitation this winter have forced me to feel that this",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 32,
      "text": "observation of mine should be sent somewhere in the interest",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 33,
      "text": "of national security.",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 34,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 35,
      "text": "I have one son in the Air Corps and another works with the",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 36,
      "text": "A.E.C. at Hanford which causes me to pray for peace, as well",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 37,
      "text": "as the fact that as a minister I deplore the waste and tragedy",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 38,
      "text": "of war. That is one reason that I have refrained from passing",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 39,
      "text": "on information and ideas that might incite warlike attitudes.",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 40,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 41,
      "text": "May I add these words to paragraph two. The explosion effect",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 42,
      "text": "seemed to rise to a height of about ten thousand feet.",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 43,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 44,
      "text": "Sincerely,",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 45,
      "status": "blank"
    },
